findings.title: ELFM - Exceed Limit Fees Manipulation
findings.description: The contract owner has the authority to increase fees without limit by calling the `setTaxFeePercent` function with a high percentage value.

findings.title: LTW - Liquidity to Team Wallet
findings.description: The contract transfers a lot of funds to the team wallet. These funds have been swapped from the swap & liquify feature.

findings.title: ST - Stop Transactions
findings.description: The contract owner has the authority to stop transactions for all users excluding the owner by setting `_maxTxAmount` to zero.
